WebMP3

- installation
- usage


- installation -

1. gunzip & untar in a directory of your choice, useful is a directory in your webserver documentroot
2. add your webserver user to group audio or make shure the user has the right to execute the binarys
   and is able to use your sound device
3. make shure you have installed php4
4. make shure the webserver user is able to write in your project directory
5. edit config.php

- usage -

1. open your browser and open the site
2. doubleclick on a directory opens it
3. doubleclick on a file adds it or plays it

if something is going wrong you should take a look at your logfile (defined in config.php)
